        <!-- SECTION 1: THE 2023 PROBLEM -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">The 2023 Problem</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">These outdated patterns are killing your cost per customer and pipeline efficiency</p>
            
            <div class="problem-grid">
                <div class="problem-card">
                    <h3>VSL Bloat</h3>
                    <p>30-45 minute VSLs creating drop-off before application. People aren't finishing the video, so they never apply.</p>
                    <div class="problem-impact">Impact: 40-60% lower watch-to-apply rates</div>
                </div>

                <div class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Email-First Nurture</h3>
                    <p>Email-only follow-up sequences missing mobile-first audiences. Show rates suffering because people don't check email before calls.</p>
                    <div class="problem-impact">Impact: 20-45% lower show rates vs SMS</div>
                </div>

                <div class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Multi-CTA Paralysis</h3>
                    <p>Landing pages with 5-7 different calls to action creating decision fatigue. Too many options kills conversion.</p>
                    <div class="problem-impact">Impact: 28-40% lower application rates</div>
                </div>

                <div class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Lead Magnet Bloat</h3>
                    <p>Multi-asset downloads and nested gating reducing quality applicants. Complexity filters out serious buyers.</p>
                    <div class="problem-impact">Impact: 40-110% drop in application completion</div>
                </div>

                <div class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Weak Application Gating</h3>
                    <p>Fluffy "what are your goals" questions not qualifying properly. Unqualified leads hitting your calendar.</p>
                    <div class="problem-impact">Impact: Lower close rates, wasted sales time</div>
                </div>

                <div class="problem-card">
                    <h3>Slow DM Response</h3>
                    <p>Treating DMs like customer support with 24-hour response times. Buyers going cold while waiting.</p>
                    <div class="problem-impact">Impact: 50% lower close rates vs under-10min response</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card" style="margin-top: 60px; background: rgba(240, 157, 34, 0.1); border: 3px solid var(--brand-orange);">
                <div class="card-header" style="color: var(--brand-orange);">The Result: $4,800+ CAC When It Should Be $700-$1,500</div>
                <p style="font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px); color: var(--text-secondary);">Most coaches and course creators are overpaying 3-5x for customers because they're running outdated funnel patterns from 2023.</p>
            </div>
