                            <li>Remove multi-CTA paralysis</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="impact-badge">Highest Impact Lever</div>
                </div>

                <div class="optimization-card">
                    <div class="optimization-title">Show Rate</div>
                    <div class="optimization-content">
                        SMS-first reminders consistently beat email by 20-45%. Mobile-first audiences check texts, not email.
                        <br><br>
                        <strong>How to improve:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>SMS booking confirmation</li>
                            <li>24-hour SMS reminder</li>
                            <li>3-hour SMS reminder</li>
                            <li>15-minute SMS heads up</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="impact-badge">Quick Win: +20-45%</div>
                </div>

                <div class="optimization-card">
                    <div class="optimization-title">Close Rate</div>
                    <div class="optimization-content">
                        DM velocity (response under 10 minutes) doubles close rates. Fast response = personal attention = trust.
                        <br><br>
                        <strong>How to improve:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Staff DMs like sales channel</li>
                            <li>Response goal under 10 minutes</li>
                            <li>Use qualification scripts</li>
                            <li>Track latency metrics</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="impact-badge">Game Changer: 2x Close Rate</div>
